<div xmlns:perseus="http://www.perseus.org/meta/perseus.rdfs#" xmlns:dctype="http://purl.org/dc/dcmitype/" xmlns:tufts="http://www.tufts.edu/" xmlns:alph="http://alpheios.net/namespaces/tei" class="alpheios-lex-text_container en">
    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n9602" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χαρίζομαι</span></b>  (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χάρις</span>), aor. opt. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χαρίσαιτο</span>, inf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">-ασθαι</span>,
          pass. perf. part. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κεχαρισμένος</span>, plup.
            <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κεχάριστο</span>: <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">show favor,
            gratify</span>, <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">τινί</span>, very often
          the part., <i><span class="en">Il. 4.71</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Od. 10.43</span></i>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">; τινὶ ψευδέσι</span>, ‘court favor by lies,’
            <i><span class="en">Od. 14.387</span></i>; w. acc., ‘bestow
          graciously’ or ‘abundantly,’ <i><span class="en">Il.
            11.134</span></i>; also with partitive gen., esp. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">παρεόντων</span>, ‘giving freely of her store,’ <i><span class="en">Od. 1.140</span></i>; perf. and plup. as pass.,
            <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">be dear</span> or <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">pleasing;</span>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κεχαρισμένος ἦλθεν</span>, was
            <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">welcome</span>, <i><span class="en">Od. 2.54</span></i>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">; κεχαρισμένα θεῖναι</span>, like <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χαρίσασθαι</span>, <i><span class="en">Il.
            24.661</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
